Esto, esto...

00:17:38.960 --> 00:17:39.530
Amigo.

00:17:40.240 --> 00:17:41.030
¿Cómo te llamas?

00:17:41.230 --> 00:17:42.040
Lao Caihua.

00:17:42.270 --> 00:17:43.210
